					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 8.3847em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.15em;">1.1. 艺术手法 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 10.0902em; left:5.9055em;z-index:43; "><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">修辞手法（攻于文<span class="stl_17">字</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）：</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">比喻、比拟（拟人、拟物，把…<span class="stl_17">当作…</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）、</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">夸张、借代（<span class="stl_17">简 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 11.212em; left:6.7544em;z-index:69; "><span class="stl_06 stl_19">练含蓄）、反问（加强语气、强烈情<span class="stl_20">感</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）、</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">设问（开篇：问题引入，带<span class="stl_17">动全篇</span></span><span class="stl_16">†</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">中间： &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 12.6582em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_21">承上启下</span><span class="stl_16 stl_21">†</span><span class="stl_06 stl_21">结尾：深化主题，令人回味）、双关（含蓄幽默，加深语义，深<span class="stl_20">刻印象。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 14.4287em; left:6.2556em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">“</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 14.4287em; left:7.2531em;z-index:146; "><span class="stl_06 stl_19">丝（思）方尽”、道是无晴却有晴（<span class="stl_20">情</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">））</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">、互文、通感（用一种感觉表现（<span class="stl_17">转换到） &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 15.8749em; left:6.7544em;z-index:194; "><span class="stl_06 stl_14">另一种。生动活泼，新奇独特。区别感官结合：很<span class="stl_17">多感觉一锅炖</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）、</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">列锦（名词排列<span class="stl_17">： &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 17.3211em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">烘托气氛，创造意<span class="stl_17">境） &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 18.7673em; left:5.9055em;z-index:224; "><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">描写手法（攻于画<span class="stl_17">面</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）：</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.07em;">正（外语动心神 细节）侧（衬托、对比、环境、正反衬） &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 20.2135em; left:6.7544em;z-index:282; "><span class="stl_06 stl_21">结合、动静结合、虚实结合（回忆想象）<span class="stl_20">、点面结合（详细与概括结合</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）、</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">感官结合 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 21.6596em; left:6.2556em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">（</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 21.6596em; left:7.2531em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_20">视听味嗅触）、远近结合（视<span class="stl_19">野角度距离等） &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 22.64em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_16">•</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 26.9785em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_16">•</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 22.7814em; left:6.7544em;z-index:345; "><span class="stl_06 stl_19" style="word-spacing:0.06em;">抒情手法（直接/间接）： 直抒胸臆<span class="stl_20">（直接抒情）</span></span><span class="stl_16 stl_20" style="word-spacing:0.06em;">†</span><span class="stl_16 stl_20" style="word-spacing:0.31em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_19" style="word-spacing:0.31em;">借景抒情（先有情，再有<span class="stl_20">景）、 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 24.552em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_20">融情于景（好像景物自己可以抒发情感）、情景<span class="stl_19">交融（前两者的结合）、以景结情（结 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 25.6738em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">尾写景，留白想象<span class="stl_17">）</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">托物言志（借物抒<span class="stl_17">情）</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">用典（拓展意境，含蓄，字少<span class="stl_17">意丰） &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 27.12em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_22" style="word-spacing:-0.1em;">表现手法： 想象：由已知事物想到新的、其他class的事物</span><span class="stl_16 stl_22" style="word-spacing:-0.03em;">†</span><span class="stl_16 stl_22" style="word-spacing:0.22em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_22" style="word-spacing:0.22em;">联想：由已知事物<span class="stl_17">想到 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 28.5662em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">类似的、同类的事<span class="stl_17">物</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">对比</span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">衬托：有正衬、反<span class="stl_17">衬</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">借古讽今：怀古咏史诗中<span class="stl_17">常见</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 30.0123em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">对写：即曲笔，从对方视角写，不直抒自己情感。情深<span class="stl_17">义厚、回味遐想</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">以小见大<span class="stl_17">： &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 31.7829em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">个别→一般，局部→整<span class="stl_17">体。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>

					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 18.2886em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">照应前文、承上启下、推动情节、陡生波澜、意料之外、情理之<span class="stl_17">中、卒章显志、深化 &nbsp;</span></span></div>

					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 21.1809em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">人物：突出人物形象、表现人物心理、凸显人物性格、丰<span class="stl_17">富人物形象等。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 22.6271em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">环境：描写自然环境、暗示社会环境、使环境更<span class="stl_17">具典型性等。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 24.0733em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">读者：激发阅读兴趣、引发读者思考、留下<span class="stl_17">想象空间等。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 25.5195em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">主题：丰富、深化和突出主<span class="stl_17">题等。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 27.7537em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.16em;">2.5. 人称 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 29.4592em; left:5.9055em;z-index:387; "><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">第一人称：真实性，拉近与读者距离，便于抒情，<span class="stl_17">推动情节发展</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">。“</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">我”=作者本<span class="stl_17">人/ &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 30.9054em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">主人公/见证<span class="stl_17">者 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 32.3515em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">第二人称：语言亲切自然，便<span class="stl_17">于抒情 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 33.7977em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">第三人称：上帝视角，自由灵活，客观公正地看待文章全局，全<span class="stl_17">面反映问题，不受时 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 35.2439em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">间和空间的限制。讲述者，非参与者、见证<span class="stl_17">者、亲历者 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 37.4781em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.16em;">2.6. 视角 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 39.1836em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">全知视角：叙述人对整个故事都了如指掌，一<span class="stl_17">般第三人称。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.6298em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">有限视角：见证人、儿童、动物。叙述人所知受自身的限制，读<span class="stl_17">者需要思考才能理解 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 42.076em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">故事，一般第一人<span class="stl_17">称。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 44.0708em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">传统小说一般采用全知视角，而现代小说一般运用有限视角，也<span class="stl_17">存在两者结合或相互 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 45.5169em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">转换的情况<span class="stl_17">。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 47.7511em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.15em;">2.7. 段落作用 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 50.1449em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06">2</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 50.1449em; left:6.4043em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.16em;">.7.1. 开头段 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 51.6908em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">悬念式开头：造成悬念，引出下文…，引起读者思考，激发读者<span class="stl_17">阅读兴趣。突出人物 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 53.137em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">形象。揭示主题<span class="stl_17">。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 54.5832em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.28em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.28em;">写景式开头：交代故事发生背景（时间地点人物）。渲染气氛，烘托人物<span class="stl_20">心情。奠定 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 56.0294em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">感情基调。为下文作铺<span class="stl_17">垫。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 58.0242em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">悬念、伏笔、照应、铺垫、抑扬、对比、衬托、突转、<span class="stl_17">以……话题引入 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 60.2584em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06">2</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 60.2584em; left:6.4043em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.16em;">.7.2. 中间段 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 61.8043em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">结构上：呼应（承接）前文情节，揭示前文悬念，引出后文情<span class="stl_17">节，为下文情节/抒 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 63.2505em; left:6.7544em;z-index:819; "><span class="stl_06 stl_14">情/议论做铺垫（近、明显）/埋伏笔<span class="stl_17">（远、隐晦</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">），</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">承上启下 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 65.9495em; left:24.5538em;"><span class="stl_06">5</span></div>
					<div id="5_0" style="position:absolute;top:14.4631em;left:5.9055em;">&nbsp;</div>
					<div id="5_1" style="position:absolute;top:26.9204em;left:5.9055em;">&nbsp;</div>
					<div id="5_2" style="position:absolute;top:36.6448em;left:5.9055em;">&nbsp;</div>
					<div id="5_3" style="position:absolute;top:46.9178em;left:5.9055em;">&nbsp;</div>
					<div id="5_4" style="position:absolute;top:49.3116em;left:5.9055em;">&nbsp;</div>
					<div id="5_5" style="position:absolute;top:59.4251em;left:5.9055em;">&nbsp;</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="stl_02">
			<div class="stl_26">
				<img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="" class="stl_27">
			</div>
			<div class="stl_view">
				<div class="stl_03 stl_04">
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 5.8314em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">内容上：表现人物性格，丰富人物形象，表<span class="stl_17">现小说主题 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 8.0656em; left:6.4043em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.16em;">.7.3. 结尾段 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 8.0656em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06">2</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 9.6115em; left:5.9055em;z-index:47; "><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">出人意料式（欧亨<span class="stl_17">利式</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）：</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">与前文伏笔相照应，情理之中。突出人物形<span class="stl_17">象。使平淡的 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 11.0577em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">故事陡生波澜，行文富有变化，撞击读者心灵，具有震撼人心的<span class="stl_17">力量，耐人寻味。有 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 12.5039em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">利于表现/丰富主<span class="stl_17">题。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 13.95em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">戛然而止式：留白，引起读者想象，留下广阔艺术想象空间，耐<span class="stl_17">人寻味。为读者艺术 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 15.3962em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">再创造（二创）留下空<span class="stl_17">间。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 16.8424em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">悲剧式：与前文美好情景形成鲜明对比，有强烈的艺术感染力。<span class="stl_17">更好塑造人物性格。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 18.2886em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">表现/深化主题。令人感动惋惜，引发读者思考<span class="stl_17">，耐人寻味。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 19.7348em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">喜剧式：情感体验：符合主人公/作者/读者的理想愿望和情感<span class="stl_17">追求，使读者有阅读 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 21.1809em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">的欣慰和愉悦。主题：彰显人性（真善美、道德、法治、社会、<span class="stl_17">人民、真理、宽容、 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 22.6271em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">智慧）的巨大力量，反映人民/作者对幸福美好人生的向往，表<span class="stl_17">现/深化主题。表达 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 24.0733em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">效果：给读者留下广阔的想象空间，<span class="stl_17">耐人寻味。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 26.0681em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">欧亨利、悲剧、大团圆、戛然而止、写景<span class="stl_17">、首尾呼应 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 28.3023em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.15em;">2.8. 叙述顺序 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 29.6834em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">顺序：脉络分明，层次清晰，层层深入，给人<span class="stl_17">以清晰的印象</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">倒叙：设置悬念，<span class="stl_17">引人 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 31.1296em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">入胜</span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">插叙：补充说明，丰富文章内容，使情节完整，结构严谨。<span class="stl_17">铺垫，照应呼应。 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 32.5758em; left:5.9055em;z-index:513; "><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">去掉后不影响故事完整性。一般在中部<span class="stl_17">，补充内容</span></span><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">补叙（追叙</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）：</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">对上文内容补充<span class="stl_17">交 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 34.3463em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">代/揭露影响事件发展的关键伏线，使之真相大白，产生强烈的戏<span class="stl_17">剧效果。更好体现主 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 35.7925em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">题，结构完整，行文跌宕起伏，有出人意料的效果。去掉后会影<span class="stl_17">响故事完整性。一般 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 36.9143em; left:5.9055em;z-index:704; "><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">在结尾，补全结构。一是在文<span class="stl_17">章最后</span></span><span class="stl_16 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.26em;">† </span><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">平叙（平行叙<span class="stl_17">述</span></span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.5em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_18">）：</span><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:0em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_06 stl_14">同一时间不同地点发生<span class="stl_17">的多 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 38.6849em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0em;">件事，先叙一件，再叙一件。可将纷繁复杂的情节/事件 写得<span class="stl_17">眉目清楚，有条不紊 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.1311em; left:5.4068em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">（</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.1311em; left:6.4043em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">使小说脉络、条理清<span class="stl_17">晰） &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 42.3653em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.16em;">2.9. 标题 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 44.759em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06">2</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 44.759em; left:6.4043em;"><span class="stl_06" style="word-spacing:-0.25em;">.9.1. 标题作用 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 46.305em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">时间、地点、环境为题：点明时间地点、创设故事情境、渲染气<span class="stl_17">氛，简洁醒目、生动 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 47.7511em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">形象、富有诗<span class="stl_17">意 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 49.1973em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:0.25em;">物象为题：线索、概括故事情节、画龙点睛、揭示主题、多<span class="stl_17">重含义、寄托情感 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 50.6435em; left:5.9055em;"><sup><span class="stl_16 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.28em;">• </span></sup><span class="stl_06 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.28em;">形象特征为题（长鼻子匹诺曹）：铺展情节，照应细节，对比，讽刺，突<span class="stl_20">出人物个性 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 52.0897em; left:6.7544em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">化特征，强化某种效果，设置悬念，激发读<span class="stl_17">者阅读兴趣 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 54.3239em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06">2</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 54.3239em; left:6.4043em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.15em;">.9.2. 标题好处/意蕴 &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 55.8698em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">表达技巧（双关、比喻、拟人、反讽、引用）+表层含义+深层<span class="stl_17">含义（引申义、比喻 &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 57.316em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_06 stl_14">义、象征义<span class="stl_17">） &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="top: 59.5502em; left:5.9055em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_14" style="word-spacing:-0.14em;">2.10. 环境描写作用 &nbsp;</span></div>

a {
  --text-decoration: none;
}
a.secondary,
a.contrast {
  --text-decoration: underline;
}

small {
  --font-size: 0.875em;
}

h1,
h2,
h3,
h4,
h5,
h6 {
  --font-weight: 700;
}

h1 {
  --font-size: 2rem;
  --typography-spacing-vertical: 3rem;
}

h2 {
  --font-size: 1.75rem;
  --typography-spacing-vertical: 2.625rem;
}

h3 {
  --font-size: 1.5rem;
  --typography-spacing-vertical: 2.25rem;
}

h4 {
  --font-size: 1.25rem;
  --typography-spacing-vertical: 1.874rem;
}

h5 {
  --font-size: 1.125rem;
  --typography-spacing-vertical: 1.6875rem;
}

[type="checkbox"],
[type="radio"] {
  --border-width: 2px;
}

[type="checkbox"][role="switch"] {
  --border-width: 3px;
}

thead th,
thead td,
tfoot th,
tfoot td {
  --border-width: 3px;
}

:not(thead, tfoot) > * > td {
  --font-size: 0.875em;
}

pre,
code,
kbd,
samp {
  --font-family: "Menlo", "Consolas", "Roboto Mono", "Ubuntu Monospace",
    "Noto Mono", "Oxygen Mono", "Liberation Mono", monospace,
    "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";
}

kbd {
  --font-weight: bolder;
}

[data-theme="light"],
#mount:not([data-theme="dark"]) {

  [data-tooltip][data-placement="left"]:hover::after {
    animation-duration: 0.2s;
    animation-name: tooltip-slide-left;
  }
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="left"]:focus::after,
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="left"]:hover::after {
    animation-name: tooltip-caret-slide-left;
  }
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="right"]:focus::before,
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="right"]:focus::after,
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="right"]:hover::before,
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="right"]:hover::after {
    animation-duration: 0.2s;
    animation-name: tooltip-slide-right;
  }
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="right"]:focus::after,
  [data-tooltip][data-placement="right"]:hover::after {
    animation-name: tooltip-caret-slide-right;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-slide-top {
  from {
    transform: translate(-50%, 0.75rem);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(-50%, -0.25rem);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-caret-slide-top {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  50% {
    transform: translate(-50%, -0.25rem);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(-50%, 0rem);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-slide-bottom {
  from {
    transform: translate(-50%, -0.75rem);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(-50%, 0.25rem);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-caret-slide-bottom {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  50% {
    transform: translate(-50%, -0.5rem);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(-50%, -0.3rem);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-slide-left {
  from {
    transform: translate(0.75rem, -50%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(-0.25rem, -50%);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-caret-slide-left {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  50% {
    transform: translate(0.05rem, -50%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(0.3rem, -50%);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-slide-right {
  from {
    transform: translate(-0.75rem, -50%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(0.25rem, -50%);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
@keyframes tooltip-caret-slide-right {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  50% {
    transform: translate(-0.05rem, -50%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translate(-0.3rem, -50%);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

/**
 * Accessibility & User interaction
 */
[aria-controls] {
  cursor: pointer;
}

[aria-disabled="true"],
[disabled] {
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

[aria-hidden="false"][hidden] {
  display: initial;
}

[aria-hidden="false"][hidden]:not(:focus) {
  clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
  position: absolute;
}

a,
area,
button,
input,
label,
select,
summary,
textarea,
[tabindex] {
  -ms-touch-action: manipulation;
}

[dir="rtl"] {
  direction: rtl;
}

/**
* Reduce Motion Features
*/
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *:not([aria-busy="true"]),
  :not([aria-busy="true"])::before,
  :not([aria-busy="true"])::after {
    background-attachment: initial !important;
    animation-duration: 1ms !important;
    animation-delay: -1ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    scroll-behavior: auto !important;
    transition-delay: 0s !important;
    transition-duration: 0s !important;
  }
}
